                <ul class="tabcon">
                    <li>Overall household spending has increased for <span style="color: #933993;">58%</span> of families</li>
                    <li>Essentials like personal care & household items see increased spending from <span style="color: #933993;">48%</span> of families, a 5 percentage point rise from last month</li>
