                    <li>Video Streaming Platform/OTT viewership data reveals varied content preferences across different age groups, with specific interests in comedy, long-form, and short-form videos</li>
                    <li><span style="color: #933993;">65%</span> of respondents acknowledge improvements in road conditions in the last ten years</li>
